            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Don't go by the given 5* rating, these are given by their own people.\nPlease don't get impressed by the building of this school, internal reality is totally different. Here teachers gets change in every few months within one session and children and parents face a lot of trouble. When I checked the reason, I got to know the entire focus of this school is to deduct salary of their staff, they find every possible reason to deduct the salary of their teachers. Also, if we talk about the salary, they hire teachers in 20k or max 25k per month which is equivalent to the fee of 2 or 3 students then how a teacher should feel motivated to teach and help our children. They keep the degrees of teachers to blackmail them later.\nAlso, they just provide manual so that no chapter reading is required and teacher can directly ask children to fill the notebooks",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
