            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I am delighted to write a  review about Alpine Convent School . Having been a part of this institution ,I can confidently say that it offers an exceptional educational experience.\n\nOne of the standout features of the School is its dedicated and highly qualified faculty. The teachers are not only knowledgeable in their respective fields but also passionate about imparting knowledge to their students.\nIt provides a well-rounded education that goes beyond academics. The school offers a wide range of extracurricular activities, including sports, arts, and clubs, allowing students to explore their interests and develop important life skills.\nFurthermore, Alpine prioritizes the safety and well-being of its students.  This aspect provides peace of mind to parents and allows students to focus on their education without any concerns.\n\nI highly recommend Alpine Convent School to anyone seeking a school that values excellence, holistic development and community spirit.\n\nThanks",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
